Belgacom Fires Fagard; CEO Bellens May Hire Her Outside Company

-- B y   J o h n   M a r t e n s
-- 
2011-09-15T20:28:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/belgacom-fires-fagard-ceo-bellens-may-hire-her-outside-company.html
Belgacom SA (BELG)  said Chief Executive
Officer Didier Bellens and the chairman of the board reached an
agreement to end the contract of Concetta Fagard, Bellens’s
personal assistant.  Bellens may hire Fagard “in another capacity” outside
Belgacom, the Brussels-based telephone company said in an e-
mailed statement. Belgacom also said Astrid De Lathauwer, head
of human resources, will leave the company.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Martens at 
 jmartens1@bloomberg.net  